    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Rare Find \u2013 Mint Condition & Ready to Wow!** Stop scrolling \u2014 this one is the real deal! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition, meaning it looks, drives, and presents like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Everything is in top-notch shape: the interior is immaculate, the exterior is flawless, and the performance is as crisp and responsive as it gets. If you've been holding out for a car you can be truly proud of, your wait is over. Opportunities like this don't come around often \u2014 come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 47000.0,
